		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><p>Read more <a href="http://www.sajaforum.org/2008/11/breaking-news-terrorists-attack-mumbai-hotels.html" target="_blank">here</a>. Mumbai friends, my thoughts and yes, even prayers (insofar as an agnostic has prayers), are with you.</p>
