<div class="post-footer">November 26th, 2008 |  Category: <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/handbasket/" title="View all posts in handbasket" rel="category tag">handbasket</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/hell/" title="View all posts in hell" rel="category tag">hell</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/india/" title="View all posts in India" rel="category tag">India</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/religion/" title="View all posts in religion" rel="category tag">religion</a> | <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2008/11/26/terror-attacks-in-mumbai/#respond" class="comments-link"  title="Comment on Terror attacks in Mumbai">Leave a comment</a> </div>
